# Dev Server Rule

- Always start local development with `npm run start:dev` (or aliases `npm run up` / `npm run run:all`).
- Do not run `npm run dev` in multiple terminals at the same time.
- If restart is needed: stop the running server first (`Ctrl+C`), then start again.
- Use one server on `http://localhost:3000` and switch by route:
  - Master: `/master/login`
  - Tenant app: `/login` or `/dashboard`
